{"type":"user","uuid":"b6e476ea-e460-4fad-a972-760f5b107bab","session_id":"40f278db-8cd3-4168-987a-9ae4d774284e","message":{"content":[{"type":"tool_result","tool_use_id":"019ce342eb6a72b457a92efe7892749d","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Successfully created and wrote to new file: /Users/loneyu/SelfProjects/PrizmClaw/.prizmkit/specs/009-general-command-executor/plan.md"}],"is_error":false}],"role":"user"},"parent_tool_use_id":"019ce342eb6a72b457a92efe7892749d","__timestamp":"2026-03-12T18:16:11.862Z","_requestId":"28efb2d2223148a8a0cf1e344695caa8"}
{"type":"assistant","uuid":"20260313021617a8da9f746f8d4c22","session_id":"40f278db-8cd3-4168-987a-9ae4d774284e","message":{"id":"20260313021617a8da9f746f8d4c22","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"019ce3438468cb2d54b0df807a845cd5","name":"Write","input":{"content":"# Tasks - F-009: General Command Executor\n\n## Phase 1: Configuration & Infrastructure\n\n- [ ] **T-1.1**: Add new config variables to src/config.js\n  - Add COMMAND_BLACKLIST env var parsing\n  - Add HIGH_RISK_KEYWORDS env var parsing\n  - Add DIRECT_EXEC_MODE env var parsing\n  - Export commandBlacklist, highRiskKeywords, directExecMode in config object\n\n- [ ] **T-1.2**: Extend session-store.js for cwd and output pages\n  - Add #cwdBySessionKey Map\n  - Add #outputPagesBySessionKey Map\n  - Add getCwd(sessionKey) method\n  - Add setCwd(sessionKey, cwd) method\n  - Add getOutputPages(sessionKey) method\n  - Add setOutputPages(sessionKey, pages) method\n  - Add clearOutputPages(sessionKey) method\n  - Update clear() to reset cwd and output pages\n\n## Phase 2: Security Extensions\n\n- [ ] **T-2.1**: Extend system-guard.js with blacklist and high-risk detection\n  - Add checkCommandBlacklist(command, blacklist) function\n  - Add detectHighRiskKeywords(command, keywords) function\n  - Export new functions for use in command-executor-service\n\n- [ ] **T-2.2**: Update permission-guard.js for new commands\n  - Add 'cd': 'operator' to COMMAND_MIN_ROLE\n  - Add 'more': 'viewer' to COMMAND_MIN_ROLE\n  - Remove 'exec' from HIGH_RISK_COMMANDS (handled via keywords)\n\n## Phase 3: Core Services\n\n- [ ] **T-3.1**: Create output-pager-service.js\n  - Implement paginateOutput(text, chunkSize = 4000)\n  - Implement storeOutputPages(sessionId, pages)\n  - Implement getNextPage(sessionId)\n  - Implement clearPages(sessionId)\n  - Write unit tests in tests/services/output-pager-service.test.js\n\n- [ ] **T-3.2**: Create command-executor-service.js\n  - Implement executeCommand({ command, sessionId, userId })\n  - Integrate blacklist check\n  - Integrate high-risk keyword detection\n  - Integrate confirmation flow for high-risk commands\n  - Integrate session cwd\n  - Use output-pager-service for long output\n  - Log to audit-log-service\n  - Write unit tests in tests/services/command-executor-service.test.js\n\n- [ ] **T-3.3**: Enhance system-exec-service.js timeout handling\n  - Add SIGKILL after SIGTERM timeout (grace period: 5s)\n  - Return timeout status in result object\n  - Add cwd parameter support\n  - Update tests\n\n## Phase 4: Command Handlers\n\n- [ ] **T-4.1**: Create /cd command handler (src/bot/commands/handlers/cd.js)\n  - Implement handleCd function\n  - Validate directory exists and is accessible\n  - Update session cwd via session-store\n  - Write unit tests in tests/bot/commands/handlers/cd.test.js\n\n- [ ] **T-4.2**: Create /more command handler (src/bot/commands/handlers/more.js)\n  - Implement handleMore function\n  - Fetch next page from output-pager-service\n  - Handle \"no more output\" scenario\n  - Write unit tests in tests/bot/commands/handlers/more.test.js\n\n- [ ] **T-4.3**: Update /exec handler in telegram.js\n  - Import command-executor-service\n  - Replace executeSystemCommand with executeCommand\n  - Handle paginated output\n\n- [ ] **T-4.4**: Add direct text mode to telegram.js\n  - Check DIRECT_EXEC_MODE config\n  - Route non-command text to exec handler when enabled\n  - Keep chat mode as default when disabled\n\n- [ ] **T-4.5**: Register new commands in telegram.js\n  - Import cd and more handlers\n  - Register /cd command\n  - Register /more command\n\n## Phase 5: Testing & Documentation\n\n- [ ] **T-5.1**: Create integration test\n  - Create tests/integration/f009-command-executor.integration.test.js\n  - Test end-to-end command execution flow\n  - Test high-risk confirmation flow\n  - Test timeout handling\n  - Test blacklist enforcement\n  - Test /cd and /more commands\n\n- [ ] **T-5.2**: Update .prizm-docs\n  - Update runtime/services.prizm with new services\n  - Update runtime/security.prizm with new security functions\n  - Update runtime/bot.prizm with new commands\n  - Add DECISIONS entry for F-009\n\n- [ ] **T-5.3**: Update .env.example\n  - Add COMMAND_BLACKLIST with example value\n  - Add HIGH_RISK_KEYWORDS with default value\n  - Add DIRECT_EXEC_MODE with description\n\n## Execution Order\n\n1. T-1.1 (config) → T-1.2 (session-store)\n2. T-2.1 (system-guard) → T-2.2 (permission-guard)\n3. T-3.1 (output-pager) → T-3.2 (command-executor) → T-3.3 (system-exec)\n4. T-4.1 (cd) → T-4.2 (more) → T-4.3 (exec) → T-4.4 (direct mode) → T-4.5 (register)\n5. T-5.1 (integration test) → T-5.2 (prizm docs) → T-5.3 (env example)\n\n## Acceptance Criteria Coverage\n\n| AC | Tasks |\n|----|-------|\n| AC-1: Execute and return stdout/stderr | T-3.2, T-4.3 |\n| AC-2: Whitelist/blacklist security | T-1.1, T-2.1, T-3.2 |\n| AC-3: Timeout with process termination | T-3.3 |\n| AC-4: Long output pagination | T-3.1, T-4.2 |\n| AC-5: /cd for working directory | T-1.2, T-4.1 |\n| AC-6: High-risk command confirmation | T-2.1, T-3.2 |\n","file_path":"/Users/loneyu/SelfProjects/PrizmClaw/.prizmkit/specs/009-general-command-executor/tasks.md"}}],"model":"glm-5.0","role":"assistant","stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"type":"message","usage":{"input_tokens":71807,"output_tokens":1392,"cache_creation_input_tokens":null,"cache_read_input_tokens":null,"cache_creation":null,"server_tool_use":null,"service_tier":null}},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"__timestamp":"2026-03-12T18:16:42.242Z","_requestId":"28efb2d2223148a8a0cf1e344695caa8"}
