e (0.049958ms)\n✔ mock-runner: createStatefulMockRunner tracks state (0.153208ms)\n✔ mock-runner: createStatefulMockRunner prevents duplicate start (0.040708ms)\n✔ mock-telegram: createMockContext creates context (0.089417ms)\n✔ mock-telegram: createMockContext applies overrides (0.030333ms)\n✔ mock-telegram: reply captures messages (0.0515ms)\n✔ mock-telegram: _getLastReply returns last reply (0.043709ms)\n✔ mock-telegram: createAdminContext sets admin permission (0.038417ms)\n✔ mock-telegram: createOperatorContext sets operator permission (0.033083ms)\n✔ mock-telegram: createViewerContext sets viewer permission (0.042875ms)\n✔ mock-telegram: createDocumentContext creates document message (0.0485ms)\n✔ mock-telegram: createCommandContext creates command message (0.033333ms)\n✔ test-state: createTestStateDir creates directory (12.354083ms)\n✔ test-state: createTestPipelineDirs creates full structure (3.967292ms)\n✔ test-state: writeTestState and readTestState work together (7.891708ms)\n✔ test-state: readTestState returns null for non-existent file (0.192334ms)\n✔ test-state: createTestPlan creates plan file (6.177834ms)\n▶ Integration: F-008 Commit Workflow\n  ▶ US-1: Telegram Commit Trigger\n    ✔ AC-1.1: /commit command triggers commit flow (6.307875ms)\n    ✔ AC-1.2: --message parameter specifies commit message (1.427958ms)\n    ✔ AC-1.3: --amend requires admin permission (checked at handler level) (1.502542ms)\n    ✔ AC-1.4: Returns commit hash and change summary (3.277875ms)\n  ✔ US-1: Telegram Commit Trigger (13.385709ms)\n  ▶ US-2: Pre-Commit Validation\n    ✔ AC-2.1: Rejects commit when pipeline is running (1.447333ms)\n    ✔ AC-2.2: Rejects commit when tests failed (1.989916ms)\n\nStderr: (empty)\nExit Code: 0\nSignal: (none)"}],"is_error":false}],"role":"user"},"parent_tool_use_id":"019ce343eca564fbbcc1a3941371d2af","__timestamp":"2026-03-12T18:19:56.378Z","_requestId":"28efb2d2223148a8a0cf1e344695caa8"}
