{"type":"user","uuid":"ef067d13-2a5c-4014-92e6-bf27d46cca79","session_id":"40f278db-8cd3-4168-987a-9ae4d774284e","message":{"content":[{"type":"tool_result","tool_use_id":"call_1505d1d4757244dcab3b6bbc","content":[{"type":"text","text":"   1→---\n   2→name: prizm-dev-team-reviewer\n   3→description: PrizmKit-integrated quality reviewer. Uses prizmkit.analyze for cross-document consistency, prizmkit.code-review for spec compliance and code quality, and writes integration tests. Use when performing analysis, testing, or code review.\n   4→tools: Read, Write, Edit, Bash, Glob, Grep, TaskCreate, TaskGet, TaskUpdate, TaskList, SendMessage\n   5→model: inherit\n   6→skills: prizmkit-code-review, prizmkit-analyze, prizmkit-prizm-docs\n   7→---\n   8→\n   9→你是 **Reviewer Agent**，PrizmKit-integrated Multi-Agent 软件开发协作团队的质量审查员。\n  10→\n  11→### 核心身份\n  12→\n  13→你是团队的\"质检员 + 校对员\"——不生产产品但确保质量，负责两个阶段的工作：\n  14→1. **交叉校验（Phase 4）**: 在实现前用 `prizmkit.analyze` 检查 spec/plan/tasks 的一致性\n  15→2. **评审（Phase 6）**: 在实现后用 `prizmkit.code-review` 检查代码质量，编写和执行集成测试\n  16→\n  17→### 项目上下文\n  18→\n  19→项目文档在 `.prizm-docs/`。审查前先读 `root.prizm` 了解项目规则（RULES）、模式（PATTERNS）和已知陷阱（TRAPS），需要时读取模块级文档。\n  20→\n  21→### 制品路径\n  22→\n  23→| 路径 | 用途 |\n  24→|------|------|\n  25→| `.prizm-docs/` | 项目知识层 — 规则、模式、已知陷阱 |\n  26→| `.prizmkit/specs/###-feature-name/` | 功能制品 — spec.md / plan.md / tasks.md |\n  27→\n  28→### 必须做 (MUST)\n  29→\n  30→1. Phase 4 时运行 `prizmkit.analyze` 做交叉一致性校验\n  31→2. Phase 6 时运行 `prizmkit.code-review` 做规格合规和代码质量审查\n  32→3. Phase 6 时编写和执行集成测试，验证模块间交互\n  33→4. 验证实际实现是否符合 plan.md 中的接口设计\n  34→5. 验证跨模块数据流的完整性和正确性\n  35→6. 测试边界条件和异常路径\n  36→7. 检查代码是否符合 `.prizm-docs/` RULES 和 PATTERNS\n  37→8. 审查是**只读操作**（Phase 4 和 Phase 6 的审查部分不修改代码文件）\n  38→9. 集成测试用例必须覆盖 spec.md 定义的所有用户故事\n  39→\n  40→### 绝不做 (NEVER)\n  41→\n  42→- 不编写实现代码（Dev 的职责）\n  43→- 不分解任务（PM 的职责）\n  44→- 不进行任务调度（Coordinator 的职责）\n  45→- **不执行任何 git 操作**（git commit / git add / git reset / git push 均禁止）\n  46→- 不使用 TaskCreate/TaskUpdate 创建或修改 Orchestrator 层的任务（Task 工具仅用于内部进度追踪，且任务 ID 在各 agent 子会话中互不共享）\n  47→\n  48→### 行为规则\n  49→\n  50→```\n  51→REV-01: Phase 4 使用 prizmkit.analyze 做交叉校验\n  52→REV-02: Phase 6 使用 prizmkit.code-review 做代码审查\n  53→REV-03: 每个发现必须引用具体的文件路径和行号\n  54→REV-04: CRITICAL 级别发现必须包含具体的修复建议\n  55→REV-05: 最多 30 个发现（保持可操作性）\n  56→REV-06: Spec compliance 失败始终为 HIGH 或 CRITICAL\n  57→REV-07: 安全发现始终为 HIGH 或 CRITICAL\n  58→REV-08: 集成测试必须覆盖 spec.md 所有用户故事\n  59→REV-09: 审查代码是否符合 .prizm-docs/ PATTERNS 和 RULES\n  60→REV-10: 禁止使用 timeout 命令（macOS 不兼容）。运行测试时直接使用 node --test 或 npm test，不加 timeout 前缀\n  61→```\n  62→\n  63→### Phase 4 工作流程：交叉校验\n  64→\n  65→**前置条件**: PM 已完成 spec.md / plan.md / tasks.md\n  66→\n  67→1. 调用 `prizmkit.analyze` skill（**不是 CLI 命令**，使用 Skill 工具或 `/prizmkit-analyze` 指令调用）\n  68→   - 输入: spec.md, plan.md, tasks.md\n  69→   - 6 个检测通道: 重复检测、歧义检测、不完整检测、Prizm 规则对齐、覆盖缺口、不一致性\n  70→   - 输出: 一致性分析报告（仅对话输出）\n  71→   - 若 Skill 工具不可用，则根据 6 个检测通道手动执行交叉一致性分析\n  72→2. 如发现 CRITICAL 问题，报告给 Coordinator 退回 PM 修复\n  73→3. 发送 COMPLETION_SIGNAL（含分析结果）\n  74→\n  75→### Phase 6 工作流程：评审\n  76→\n  77→**前置条件**: Dev 已完成实现，所有任务标记 `[x]`\n  78→\n  79→1. 读取 `.prizm-docs/root.prizm`，重点关注 RULES 和 PATTERNS\n  80→2. 运行 `prizmkit.code-review`（只读）\n  81→   - 6 个审查维度: 规格符合度、计划遵循度、代码质量、安全性、一致性、测试覆盖\n  82→   - 判定: PASS | PASS WITH WARNINGS | NEEDS FIXES\n  83→3. 编写和执行集成测试:\n  84→   - 接口合规性（请求格式、响应格式）\n  85→   - 跨模块数据流完整性\n  86→   - 用户故事验收标准（来自 spec.md）\n  87→   - 边界条件和异常路径\n  88→4. 生成统一评审报告\n  89→5. 发送 COMPLETION_SIGNAL（含判定结果）\n  90→\n  91→### 判定标准\n  92→\n  93→| 判定 | 条件 | 后续动作 |\n  94→|------|------|---------|\n  95→| **PASS** | 无 CRITICAL 或 HIGH 发现 | 进入下一阶段 |\n  96→| **PASS_WITH_WARNINGS** | 无 CRITICAL，有 HIGH 发现 | 记录待改进项，可进入下一阶段 |\n  97→| **NEEDS_FIXES** | 存在 CRITICAL 发现 | 退回 Dev 修复后重新评审 |\n  98→\n  99→### 严重级别\n 100→\n 101→| 级别 | 定义 | 示例 |\n 102→|------|------|------|\n 103→| CRITICAL | 安全风险或严重架构问题 | SQL 注入、硬编码密钥 |\n 104→| HIGH | 影响可维护性的显著问题 | 规格不符、大量重复代码 |\n 105→| MEDIUM | 代码质量改进点 | 命名不统一、缺少注释 |\n 106→| LOW | 风格建议 | 格式微调、可选优化 |\n 107→\n 108→### 异常处理\n 109→\n 110→| 场景 | 策略 |\n 111→|------|------|\n 112→| analyze 发现 CRITICAL | 报告 Coordinator → 退回 PM 修复 |\n 113→| code-review 发现 CRITICAL | 报告 Coordinator → 退回 Dev 修复 |\n 114→| 集成测试失败 | 分类严重级别 → ISSUE_REPORT → Coordinator 派发给 Dev |\n 115→| 审查发现超过 30 个 | 只保留最严重的 30 个 |\n 116→| Prizm RULES 违规 | 自动标记为 CRITICAL |\n 117→\n 118→### 通信规则\n 119→\n 120→允许 Agent 之间直接通信，但关键消息和结论必须通知 Coordinator。\n 121→- 发送 COMPLETION_SIGNAL（含判定结果）标志完成\n 122→- 发送 ISSUE_REPORT 报告 CRITICAL 发现\n 123→- 接收 TASK_ASSIGNMENT 获取分配的工作\n 124→"}],"is_error":false}],"role":"user"},"parent_tool_use_id":"019ce354b726b8a4df5dbec4c5680ecb","__timestamp":"2026-03-12T18:35:15.062Z","_requestId":"28efb2d2223148a8a0cf1e344695caa8"}
{"type":"user","uuid":"07b37759-2944-4109-9878-bebf263998c7","session_id":"40f278db-8cd3-4168-987a-9ae4d774284e","message":{"content":[{"type":"tool_result","tool_use_id":"call_5c479bac76684194994d6e34","content":[{"type":"text","text":"   1→# Context Snapshot - F-009: General Command Executor\n   2→\n   3→## Section 1 - Feature Brief\n   4→\n   5→### Feature Description\n   6→通用命令执行引擎，将 PrizmClaw 从纯 pipeline 控制工具升级为通用远程 CLI 助手。用户在 Telegram 中发送任意 shell 命令（如 ls、git status、npm run build 等），Bot 在电脑端执行并将 stdout/stderr 回传。\n   7→\n   8→核心能力：\n   9→- 基于现有 ENABLE_SYSTEM_EXEC 与 ALLOWED_COMMAND_PREFIXES 配置扩展，支持可配置的命令白名单/黑名单安全策略\n  10→- 命令执行有超时保护（SYSTEM_EXEC_TIMEOUT_MS），超时后自动 SIGTERM → SIGKILL 并通知用户\n  11→- 长输出自动截断至 Telegram 消息长度限制并支持 /more 分页查看剩余内容\n  12→- 支持通过 /cd 命令切换工作目录且目录状态在用户会话内保持\n  13→- 命令入口格式：直接发送文本即当作 shell 命令执行（当 ENABLE_SYSTEM_EXEC=true），或使用 /exec <cmd> 前缀显式调用\n  14→- 需要与 F-006 的权限系统集成，高风险命令（rm -rf、sudo 等）需要二次确认\n  15→\n  16→### Acceptance Criteria\n  17→1. 用户发送 shell 命令，Bot 在电脑端执行并返回 stdout/stderr 结果\n  18→2. 支持可配置的命令白名单/黑名单安全策略，黑名单命令直接拒绝并提示原因\n  19→3. 命令执行有超时保护，超时后自动终止进程并向用户返回超时提示\n  20→4. 长输出（超过 Telegram 4096 字符限制）自动截断并支持 /more 分页查看\n  21→5. 支持通过 /cd 切换工作目录，目录状态在用户会话内保持\n  22→6. 高风险命令（含 rm -rf、sudo、kill 等关键词）执行前需用户二次确认\n  23→\n  24→### Dependencies\n  25→- F-001 - Project Infrastructure Setup (completed)\n  26→- F-006 - Safety and Permission Guard (completed)\n  27→\n  28→---\n  29→\n  30→## Section 2 - Project Structure\n  31→\n  32→```\n  33→src/\n  34→├── adapters/\n  35→│   └── codebuddy.js\n  36→├── bot/\n  37→│   ├── telegram.js          # Main bot factory\n  38→│   └── commands/\n  39→│       ├── index.js         # Command router\n  40→│       ├── parser.js        # Command parser\n  41→│       ├── registry.js      # Command registry\n  42→│       ├── validator.js     # Parameter validator\n  43→│       ├── formatter.js     # Error formatter\n  44→│       ├── help.js          # Help text generator\n  45→│       └── handlers/        # Individual command handlers\n  46→│           ├── pipeline.js\n  47→│           ├── bugfix.js\n  48→│           ├── planner.js\n  49→│           ├── status.js\n  50→│           ├── logs.js\n  51→│           ├── stop.js\n  52→│           ├── plan.js\n  53→│           ├── audit.js\n  54→│           ├── commit.js\n  55→│           └── commits.js\n  56→├── http/\n  57→│   └── server.js\n  58→├── pipeline-infra/\n  59→│   ├── config-loader.js\n  60→│   └── script-runner.js\n  61→├── routes/\n  62→│   └── api-routes.js\n  63→├── security/\n  64→│   ├── index.js\n  65→│   ├── guard.js             # User authorization\n  66→│   ├── permission-guard.js  # Role hierarchy & command auth\n  67→│   ├── param-sanitizer.js   # Parameter sanitization\n  68→│   ├── confirmation-manager.js  # Confirmation flow\n  69→│   └── system-guard.js      # System exec authorization\n  70→├── services/\n  71→│   ├── chat-service.js\n  72→│   ├── chat-queue.js\n  73→│   ├── session-store.js     # Session state management\n  74→│   ├── system-exec-service.js  # System command execution\n  75→│   ├── audit-log-service.js    # Audit logging\n  76→│   ├── pipeline-control-service.js\n  77→│   └── ...\n  78→├── utils/\n  79→│   └── logger.js\n  80→├── config.js\n  81→└── index.js\n  82→\n  83→tests/\n  84→├── fixtures/\n  85→│   ├── plans/\n  86→│   └── states/\n  87→├── security/\n  88→│   ├── permission-guard.test.js\n  89→│   ├── param-sanitizer.test.js\n  90→│   └── confirmation-manager.test.js\n  91→├── services/\n  92→│   └── audit-log-service.test.js\n  93→├── bot/commands/\n  94→│   └── ...\n  95→└── integration/\n  96→    └── ...\n  97→```\n  98→\n  99→---\n 100→\n 101→## Section 3 - Prizm Context\n 102→\n 103→### root.prizm (L0)\n 104→```prizm\n 105→DOC_LEVEL: L0\n 106→PROJECT_NAME: PrizmClaw\n 107→PROJECT_TYPE: telegram-bridge + web-api\n 108→ADOPTION_MODE: brownfield\n 109→PLATFORM: codebuddy\n 110→LANGUAGES: JavaScript(ESM), HTML, CSS, Python, Shell\n 111→PACKAGE_MANAGER: npm\n 112→ENTRYPOINTS: src/index.js -> src/http/server.js + src/bot/telegram.js\n 113→DOC_STATUS: initialized\n 114→ASSESSMENT: ASSESSMENT.md\n 115→\n 116→MODULE_INDEX:\n 117→- runtime: src/** -> .prizm-docs/runtime.prizm\n 118→- web-ui: public/** -> .prizm-docs/web-ui.prizm\n 119→- pipeline: dev-pipeline/** -> .prizm-docs/pipeline.prizm\n 120→- dev-team: dev-team/** -> .prizm-docs/team.prizm\n 121→- project-config: package.json,.env.example,.codebuddy/settings.json,CODEBUDDY.md -> .prizm-docs/config.prizm\n 122→\n 123→DEPENDENCY_HEALTH:\n 124→- outdated_major: dotenv,express,zod\n 125→- npm_audit_prod: 0 vulnerabilities\n 126→```\n 127→\n 128→### runtime.prizm (L1) - Key Extracts\n 129→```prizm\n 130→DOC_LEVEL: L1\n 131→MODULE: runtime\n 132→PATH: src/**\n 133→DESCRIPTION: telegram + web request handling + sessioned CodeBuddy bridge\n 134→\n 135→KEY_FILES:\n 136→- src/services/system-exec-service.js\n 137→- src/security/permission-guard.js\n 138→- src/security/param-sanitizer.js\n 139→- src/security/confirmation-manager.js\n 140→- src/services/session-store.js\n 141→\n 142→INTERFACES:\n 143→- Telegram: /start, /help, /reset, /screenshot, /exec, /pipeline, /bugfix, /planner, /status, /logs, /stop, /plan, /audit, /commit, /commits, text message relay\n 144→- Security: PermissionGuard, ParamSanitizer, ConfirmationManager, AuditLogService\n 145→\n 146→TRAPS:\n 147→- system exec is disabled unless ENABLE_SYSTEM_EXEC=true\n 148→- system exec requires ALLOWED_COMMAND_PREFIXES whitelist\n 149→- high-risk commands (stop, reset, force-unlock) require admin role and confirmation\n 150→- permission check happens before command handler execution\n 151→- param sanitizer blocks path traversal and shell injection patterns\n 152→- audit logs are async written, failure does not block execution\n 153→```\n 154→\n 155→### security.prizm (L2)\n 156→```prizm\n 157→DOC_LEVEL: L2\n 158→MODULE: security\n 159→PATH: src/security/**\n 160→DESCRIPTION: Security guard layer for permission tiers, param sanitization, and confirmation flow\n 161→\n 162→ROLE_HIERARCHY:\n 163→- viewer: 0 -> can view status and logs\n 164→- operator: 1 -> can run pipelines and retry\n 165→- admin: 2 -> can stop, reset, force-unlock, exec\n 166→\n 167→COMMAND_PERMISSIONS:\n 168→- status, logs: viewer\n 169→- pipeline, bugfix, planner, retry: operator\n 170→- stop, reset, force-unlock, exec: admin\n 171→\n 172→HIGH_RISK_COMMANDS:\n 173→- stop, reset, force-unlock -> require confirmation (CONFIRM text)\n 174→- admin can skip confirmation with --force flag\n 175→\n 176→DANGEROUS_PATTERNS:\n 177→- path traversal (..)\n 178→- shell injection (backticks, $(), ${})\n 179→- command chains (||, &&, ;)\n 180→- home directory expansion (~)\n 181→- exec/eval flags\n 182→\n 183→AUDIT_LOG:\n 184→- format: JSON Lines (.jsonl)\n 185→- fields: timestamp, userId, role, action, params, result, reason, sessionId\n 186→- rotation: max 10MB per file, max 5 files\n 187→\n 188→TRAPS:\n 189→- unknown users default to 'operator' role\n 190→- permission denied is logged before returning error\n 191→- confirmation expires after 60 seconds\n 192→- audit log write failures are silent (non-blocking)\n 193→- param sanitizer rejects all dangerous patterns regardless of context\n 194→```\n 195→\n 196→---\n 197→\n 198→## Section 4 - Existing Source Files\n 199→\n 200→### src/config.js\n 201→```javascript\n 202→import 'dotenv/config';\n 203→import { z } from 'zod';\n 204→import { loadPipelineInfraConfig } from './pipeline-infra/config-loader.js';\n 205→import { resolveDaemonLogPaths } from './pipeline-infra/path-policy.js';\n 206→\n 207→const schema = z.object({\n 208→  TELEGRAM_BOT_TOKEN: z.string().optional().default(''),\n 209→  ENABLE_TELEGRAM: z.string().optional().default('true'),\n 210→  ALLOWED_USER_IDS: z.string().optional().default(''),\n 211→  CODEBUDDY_BIN: z.string().min(1).default('codebuddy'),\n 212→  CODEBUDDY_PERMISSION_FLAG: z.string().default('-y'),\n 213→  CODEBUDDY_ECHO_STDIO: z.string().optional().default('true'),\n 214→  CODEBUDDY_HEARTBEAT_MS: z.coerce.number().int().nonnegative().default(15000),\n 215→  TELEGRAM_FILE_ALLOWED_ROOTS: z.string().optional().default(''),\n 216→  TELEGRAM_FILE_CANDIDATE_DIRS: z.string().optional().default(''),\n 217→  REQUEST_TIMEOUT_MS: z.coerce.number().int().nonnegative().default(120000),\n 218→  MAX_PROMPT_CHARS: z.coerce.number().int().positive().default(8000),\n 219→  MAX_HISTORY_TURNS: z.coerce.number().int().positive().default(10),\n 220→  WEB_HOST: z.string().default('127.0.0.1'),\n 221→  WEB_PORT: z.coerce.number().int().positive().default(8787),\n 222→  ENABLE_SYSTEM_EXEC: z.string().optional().default('false'),\n 223→  ALLOWED_COMMAND_PREFIXES: z.string().optional().default(''),\n 224→  SYSTEM_EXEC_TIMEOUT_MS: z.coerce.number().int().positive().default(60000),\n 225→  LOG_LEVEL: z.enum(['fatal', 'error', 'warn', 'info', 'debug', 'trace', 'silent']).default('info'),\n 226→  // F-006: Safety and Permission Guard\n 227→  USER_PERMISSIONS: z.string().optional().default(''),\n 228→  ALLOW_ADMIN_SKIP_CONFIRM: z.string().optional().default('true'),\n 229→  AUDIT_LOG_DIR: z.string().optional().default('logs'),\n 230→  AUDIT_LOG_MAX_SIZE_MB: z.coerce.number().int().positive().default(10),\n 231→  AUDIT_LOG_MAX_FILES: z.coerce.number().int().positive().default(5)\n 232→});\n 233→\n 234→// ... parsing functions ...\n 235→\n 236→export const config = Object.freeze({\n 237→  // ... other config ...\n 238→  enableSystemExec: parseBoolean(parsed.ENABLE_SYSTEM_EXEC),\n 239→  allowedCommandPrefixes: parseCsvList(parsed.ALLOWED_COMMAND_PREFIXES),\n 240→  systemExecTimeoutMs: parsed.SYSTEM_EXEC_TIMEOUT_MS,\n 241→  // F-006: Safety and Permission Guard\n 242→  userPermissions: parseUserPermissions(parsed.USER_PERMISSIONS),\n 243→  allowAdminSkipConfirm: parseBoolean(parsed.ALLOW_ADMIN_SKIP_CONFIRM),\n 244→  auditLogDir: parsed.AUDIT_LOG_DIR,\n 245→  auditLogMaxSizeMb: parsed.AUDIT_LOG_MAX_SIZE_MB,\n 246→  auditLogMaxFiles: parsed.AUDIT_LOG_MAX_FILES,\n 247→  // ...\n 248→});\n 249→```\n 250→\n 251→### src/services/system-exec-service.js\n 252→```javascript\n 253→import { spawn } from 'node:child_process';\n 254→import { config } from '../config.js';\n 255→import { assertAllowedCommand, assertSystemExecEnabled } from '../security/system-guard.js';\n 256→\n 257→export async function executeSystemCommand(command) {\n 258→  assertSystemExecEnabled();\n 259→  const safeCommand = assertAllowedCommand(command);\n 260→\n 261→  return new Promise((resolve, reject) => {\n 262→    const child = spawn(safeCommand, {\n 263→      shell: true,\n 264→      stdio: ['ignore', 'pipe', 'pipe']\n 265→    });\n 266→\n 267→    let stdout = '';\n 268→    let stderr = '';\n 269→\n 270→    const timeout = setTimeout(() => {\n 271→      child.kill('SIGTERM');\n 272→      reject(new Error(`系统命令执行超时（>${config.systemExecTimeoutMs}ms）`));\n 273→    }, config.systemExecTimeoutMs);\n 274→\n 275→    child.stdout.on('data', (chunk) => { stdout += chunk.toString(); });\n 276→    child.stderr.on('data', (chunk) => { stderr += chunk.toString(); });\n 277→\n 278→    child.on('error', (error) => {\n 279→      clearTimeout(timeout);\n 280→      reject(new Error(`系统命令执行失败: ${error.message}`));\n 281→    });\n 282→\n 283→    child.on('close', (code) => {\n 284→      clearTimeout(timeout);\n 285→      resolve({ stdout: stdout.trim(), stderr: stderr.trim(), exitCode: code ?? -1 });\n 286→    });\n 287→  });\n 288→}\n 289→```\n 290→\n 291→### src/security/system-guard.js\n 292→```javascript\n 293→import { config } from '../config.js';\n 294→\n 295→export function assertSystemExecEnabled() {\n 296→  if (!config.enableSystemExec) {\n 297→    throw new Error('系统命令执行未启用。请在 .env 中设置 ENABLE_SYSTEM_EXEC=true。');\n 298→  }\n 299→}\n 300→\n 301→export function assertAllowedCommand(command) {\n 302→  const normalized = String(command ?? '').trim();\n 303→  if (!normalized) throw new Error('command 不能为空。');\n 304→  if (normalized.length > 2000) throw new Error('command 过长。');\n 305→  if (config.allowedCommandPrefixes.length === 0) {\n 306→    throw new Error('未配置 ALLOWED_COMMAND_PREFIXES，已拒绝执行。');\n 307→  }\n 308→  const allowed = config.allowedCommandPrefixes.some((prefix) => normalized.startsWith(prefix));\n 309→  if (!allowed) {\n 310→    throw new Error(`命令不在白名单前缀内。允许前缀: ${config.allowedCommandPrefixes.join(', ')}`);\n 311→  }\n 312→  return normalized;\n 313→}\n 314→```\n 315→\n 316→### src/security/permission-guard.js\n 317→```javascript\n 318→export const ROLE_HIERARCHY = { viewer: 0, operator: 1, admin: 2 };\n 319→\n 320→const COMMAND_MIN_ROLE = {\n 321→  status: 'viewer', logs: 'viewer', commits: 'viewer',\n 322→  pipeline: 'operator', bugfix: 'operator', planner: 'operator', retry: 'operator', commit: 'operator',\n 323→  stop: 'admin', reset: 'admin', 'force-unlock': 'admin', exec: 'admin',\n 324→  'commit-amend': 'admin', 'commit-force': 'admin'\n 325→};\n 326→\n 327→const HIGH_RISK_COMMANDS = new Set(['stop', 'reset', 'force-unlock', 'commit-amend', 'commit-force']);\n 328→\n 329→export function getUserRole(userId) { /* ... */ }\n 330→export function isAdmin(userId) { /* ... */ }\n 331→export function checkCommandPermission(userId, command) { /* ... */ }\n 332→```\n 333→\n 334→### src/security/param-sanitizer.js\n 335→```javascript\n 336→const DANGEROUS_PATTERNS = [\n 337→  { pattern: /\\.\\./, name: 'path traversal (..)' },\n 338→  { pattern: /[`$]/, name: 'shell injection ($ or `)' },\n 339→  { pattern: /~/, name: 'home directory (~)' },\n 340→  { pattern: /\\$\\(/, name: 'command substitution ($())' },\n 341→  { pattern: /\\|\\|/, name: 'command chain (||)' },\n 342→  { pattern: /&&/, name: 'command chain (&&)' },\n 343→  { pattern: /;/, name: 'command separator (;)' },\n 344→  { pattern: /\\|/, name: 'pipe (|)' },\n 345→  { pattern: /&/, name: 'ampersand (&)' },\n 346→  { pattern: /--exec\\b/, name: 'exec flag (--exec)' },\n 347→  { pattern: /--eval\\b/, name: 'eval flag (--eval)' },\n 348→  // ... more patterns\n 349→];\n 350→\n 351→export function detectDangerousPatterns(input) { /* ... */ }\n 352→export function sanitizeParam(input, options = {}) { /* ... */ }\n 353→export function validatePath(inputPath, allowedRoots) { /* ... */ }\n 354→```\n 355→\n 356→### src/security/confirmation-manager.js\n 357→```javascript\n 358→const DEFAULT_TIMEOUT_MS = 60000;\n 359→const pendingConfirmations = new Map();\n 360→\n 361→export function createConfirmation(userId, action, params, timeoutMs = DEFAULT_TIMEOUT_MS) { /* ... */ }\n 362→export function checkConfirmation(confirmId, userId) { /* ... */ }\n 363→export function confirmAction(confirmId, userId) { /* ... */ }\n 364→export function cancelConfirmation(confirmId, userId) { /* ... */ }\n 365→```\n 366→\n 367→### src/services/session-store.js\n 368→```javascript\n 369→class SessionStore {\n 370→  #messagesBySessionKey = new Map();\n 371→  #commitsBySessionKey = new Map();\n 372→\n 373→  get(sessionKey) { /* ... */ }\n 374→  append(sessionKey, role, content) { /* ... */ }\n 375→  clear(sessionKey) { /* ... */ }\n 376→  toPrompt(sessionKey, channel) { /* ... */ }\n 377→  addCommit(sessionKey, commitInfo) { /* ... */ }\n 378→  getCommits(sessionKey) { /* ... */ }\n 379→  getLastCommit(sessionKey) { /* ... */ }\n 380→}\n 381→\n 382→export const sessionStore = new SessionStore();\n 383→```\n 384→\n 385→### src/bot/telegram.js (exec command handler)\n 386→```javascript\n 387→bot.command('exec', async (ctx) => {\n 388→  try {\n 389→    ensureAllowed(ctx);\n 390→    const payload = ctx.message.text.replace('/exec', '').trim();\n 391→    if (!payload) {\n 392→      await ctx.reply('请提供命令，例如 /exec pwd');\n 393→      return;\n 394→    }\n 395→\n 396→    await ctx.reply('正在执行命令。');\n 397→    const result = await executeSystemCommand(payload);\n 398→    const output = [\n 399→      `exitCode: ${result.exitCode}`,\n 400→      result.stdout ? `stdout:\\n${result.stdout}` : 'stdout: (empty)',\n 401→      result.stderr ? `stderr:\\n${result.stderr}` : 'stderr: (empty)'\n 402→    ].join('\\n\\n');\n 403→\n 404→    await replyLargeText(ctx, output);\n 405→  } catch (error) {\n 406→    const message = error instanceof Error ? error.message : String(error);\n 407→    logger.error({ err: message }, 'Failed to exec command in telegram');\n 408→    await ctx.reply(`执行失败：${message}`);\n 409→  }\n 410→});\n 411→```\n 412→\n 413→---\n 414→\n 415→## Section 5 - Existing Tests\n 416→\n 417→### tests/security/permission-guard.test.js (excerpts)\n 418→```javascript\n 419→test('getUserRole returns operator as default for unknown users (AC-1.3)', () => {\n 420→  resetConfig();\n 421→  setConfigForTesting(createTestConfig());\n 422→  assert.equal(getUserRole('unknown-user'), 'operator');\n 423→});\n 424→\n 425→test('checkCommandPermission denies exec when ENABLE_SYSTEM_EXEC is false', () => {\n 426→  const config = createTestConfig({ enableSystemExec: false });\n 427→  config.userPermissions.set('admin-user', 'admin');\n 428→  setConfigForTesting(config);\n 429→  const result = checkCommandPermission('admin-user', 'exec');\n 430→  assert.equal(result.allowed, false);\n 431→  assert.ok(result.reason.includes('系统命令执行未启用'));\n 432→});\n 433→\n 434→test('checkCommandPermission allows admin for exec when ENABLE_SYSTEM_EXEC is true', () => {\n 435→  const config = createTestConfig({ enableSystemExec: true });\n 436→  config.userPermissions.set('admin-user', 'admin');\n 437→  setConfigForTesting(config);\n 438→  const result = checkCommandPermission('admin-user', 'exec');\n 439→  assert.equal(result.allowed, true);\n 440→});\n 441→```\n 442→\n 443→### tests/security/param-sanitizer.test.js (test patterns reference)\n 444→- Tests for path traversal detection\n 445→- Tests for shell injection detection\n 446→- Tests for command chain detection\n 447→- Tests for safe parameter handling\n 448→- Tests for targetId validation\n 449→\n 450→### tests/security/confirmation-manager.test.js (test patterns reference)\n 451→- Tests for confirmation creation